## 命名與風格

### 命名

| 類型 | 格式 |
|---|---|
| Contract | PascalCase | `ReviewRegistry` |
| Interface | `I` 前綴 | `IReviewRegistry` |
| Function | camelCase | `submitReview` |
| Event | PascalCase | `ReviewSubmitted` |
| Error | PascalCase | `ReviewNotFound` |
| Constant | UPPER_SNAKE_CASE | `MAX_REVIEW_LENGTH` |
| Storage | camelCase | `reviewCount` |

### Custom Error（不用 require string）

```solidity
// ❌ 不好（gas expensive + i18n 問題）
require(broker != address(0), "Invalid broker");

// ✅ 好
error InvalidBroker();
if (broker == address(0)) revert InvalidBroker();
```

### Event 必須

所有狀態改變必須 emit event：

```solidity
event ReviewSubmitted(
    uint256 indexed reviewId,
    address indexed author,
    bytes32 indexed brokerId,
    bytes32 contentHash,
    string ipfsCid
);
```

`indexed` 用於需要過濾的欄位（最多 3 個）。

